**Step 3 — Check your file structure in GitHub**

Your repo root should look like this — if files are in the wrong place, that's the other common cause:
```
yieldconcierge/          ← your repo root
├── pages/
├── components/
├── styles/
├── public/
├── package.json         ← must be at root, not inside a subfolder
└── next.config.js       ← must be at root
